{"type": "article", "id": 45211, "title": "H&M 退出西单大悦城，以及，Lacoste 发布“解构”款 polo 衫 | 浮华日报", "description": "我们为你挑选了今天最重要和最好看的新闻。", "date": "2017-09-15T03:09:21Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [{"id": 44089, "name": "polo"}, {"id": 1530, "name": "Lanvin"}, {"id": 2823, "name": "Lacoste"}, {"id": 671, "name": "Gucci"}, {"id": 15623, "name": "Gosha Rubchinskiy"}, {"id": 44090, "name": "sacai"}, {"id": 44091, "name": "UNDEFEATED"}, {"id": 1060, "name": "H&M"}, {"id": 1582, "name": "爱马仕"}, {"id": 44092, "name": "NEXT"}], "category": 19, "column": 8, "author": 699895, "comment_count": 6, "praise_count": 40, "image": "img/article/article_show/20170915095106Oxc0UvYgGJrjnKR1.jpg", "contents": "<h3 finallycleanhtml=\"true\" nocleanhtml=\"true\">一些重要的新闻：</h3><p><a href=\"http://finance.sina.com.cn/roll/2017-09-15/doc-ifykynia7191946.shtml\" rel=\"nofollow\"><strong>H&amp;M 退出西单大悦城</strong></a> | 日前，H&amp;M 在北京西单大悦城北端入口处的三层门店已被清空。有消息称，H&amp;M 确实是因消防问题在进行整改，在短期内并不会重新开业，未来能否重新开张还存在不确定性，且目前还没有接到会有新品牌替代 H&amp;M 入驻的消息。</p><p><a href=\"https://www.theguardian.com/business/2017/sep/14/next-morrisons-brexit-price-rises-weak-pound\" rel=\"nofollow\"><strong>英国快时尚品牌 NEXT 上半年利润下滑近 10%</strong></a> | 在截止至 7 月 29 日的 26 个星期内，NEXT 的税前利润下跌 9.5%，至 3.07 亿英镑，销售额减少了 2.2%，至 19.14 亿英镑。该集团称，NEXT 品牌业绩的下滑主要受实体店销售惨淡影响，未来将继续关闭 13 家门店。</p><p><a href=\"http://www.cpp-luxury.com/hermes-first-half-2017-profit-up-11-percent/\" rel=\"nofollow\"><strong>爱马仕上半年营收上涨 11%</strong></a> | 2017 上半年，爱马仕集团营收上涨了 11%，至 27.1 亿欧元。利润也上涨了 11%，至 6.05 亿欧元。该集团表示，已在固定汇率下实现了收入增长的目标。另外发布了全球所有区域的收入增长情况，受中国大陆市场的推动，爱马仕在除日本以外的亚太地区销售额增长了 14%，美国市场增长了 9％。</p><h3>一些值得一看的：</h3><p>为庆祝俄罗斯摇滚乐队 Mumiy Troll 的第三张大碟《Morskaya》的 20 岁生日，<a href=\"http://www.highsnobiety.com/2017/09/14/gosha-rubchinskiy-mumiy-troll/\" rel=\"nofollow\">Gosha Rubchinskiy </a>打造了一个特别的联名系列。</p><p>该系列包括搭载了 Gosha 和乐队 logo 设计的卫衣、印花 T 恤、冲浪板。Gosha 还特意前往乐队的发源地 Vladivostock 取景拍摄。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images multiple\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170915104749qAMx2updVzJvlsgP.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.663866\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170915104749rxQWYJLps06j5Rwz.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.507592\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/201709151047540fUHqdzRoBtKP2O5.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.508658\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure></div><p>Gucci 创意总监 Alessandro Michele 与美国艺术家 Trouble Andrew 合作推出的 <a href=\"v\" rel=\"nofollow\">GucciGhos</a>t，目前发布了一个银饰珠宝系列，有手链、吊坠、戒指、耳环等，艺术涂鸦风格很可爱。 </p><div class=\"com-insert-images multiple\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170915104820V8LAl9GqunUjmpDY.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/201709151048205GVrbvadZOIXpkiD.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170915104820TZX9RyjuILqgdek5.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/201709151048217oXe6yDH0j8r5tsl.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170915104821DmLUvOCG5IrZoKB3.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/201709151048212ylEV7PpkxODiGtI.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170915104821pFkeOuCLthUlSBmR.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170915104821yuZUlMIfhk8wSYHv.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure></div><p><a href=\"https://hypebeast.cn/2017/9/lacoste-x-sacai-2017-fall-winter-collection\" rel=\"nofollow\">sacai 携手 Lacoste</a>，以品牌设计师阿部千登势的招牌式解构设计，推出了一系列不正经的 polo 衫。 </p><p>该系列共有 15 款男女装单品，将于 9 月 16 日在 Lacoste 指定门店上架。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images multiple\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170915105235Iy49c3nVOxh8Pomw.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170915105235mQqvXUIMgDJBNadZ.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170915105235nEZCvTzgwMjrLcX9.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/201709151052344VAeFcDo3Ul2iMwC.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170915105235ojLhOwJk19TU7Gsm.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.665812\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170915105235jKobifxSzesrQM54.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.665812\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170915105235Fb5kBXuCt6dqRvzK.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.665812\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170915105236JdX7qxMz8NaLGZK5.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.665812\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170915105236gzBecSfEv3x05RbI.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170915105234uX5SJQxbcCjBU2Ai.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.665812\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170915105234e3d8AvYkSDOQ02HC.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.665812\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170915105234Ir3qb4VSxKpmM9H1.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170915105234aOQ4lzHibZ5cTKEt.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170915105234GvoTlwx53KMhrpCN.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure></div><p><a href=\"http://www.highsnobiety.com/2017/09/15/lanvin-matches-fashion-collection/\" rel=\"nofollow\">Lanvin </a>为英国奢侈品电商 Matches Fashion 推出了一个限定系列，包括 10 件单品，将于 9 月 21 日在 Matches Fashion 独家贩售。 </p><div class=\"com-insert-images multiple\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170915104909Jj0QWPpXdlO2Sb6G.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/201709151049113REjZn72lfImW9wG.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170915104912H37krYKtJS6XcpbG.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170915104912vHbJMjUfPlDspC9B.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/201709151049136RIHZkfM0hAaPecv.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170915104912e2EY5jJfzaNQCqIL.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure></div><p><a href=\"http://www.highsnobiety.com/2017/09/14/undefeated-nike-air-max-97/\" rel=\"nofollow\">UNDEFEATED x Nike 联名系列</a>完整公开，将于本周末在 UNDEFEATED 率先发售。</p><p>除了黑白色两款 Air Max 97 外，还有联名款服装和配饰单品。比如时下流行的腰包和跨包、袜子、连帽衫和 T 恤等。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images multiple\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170915104949sR2j5tgMvOaiH4CK.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.667000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170915104942iLeW5zthoKHx6SYQ.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170915104942HxdnI4ueF0SiqJ9R.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170915104941ypijHJAsdBMZS0Kq.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170915104941YkN8Iq3wdT5cAXeZ.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170915104937AaRcwD7uhJiXsWYZ.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/201709151049388GfC1EncDMNXS0HA.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170915104939fQn82rLhyUP6zWs0.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure></div><p><a href=\"http://www.highsnobiety.com/2017/09/14/gucci-cruise-2018-campaign/\" rel=\"nofollow\">Gucci 又发布了新的度假系列 campaign</a>。这次找来了英国摄影师 Mick Rock 掌镜，在意大利拍摄了一组不加滤镜的大片，质感挺独特的。 </p><div class=\"com-insert-images multiple\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170915105035G6OzguyxjpWIrYM9.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170915105040NAZMyiz8vnYKFBjJ.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170915105037k1zqK9frF3WU8tad.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170915105033ql9njUtkO7iDxayS.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170915105037iT0OuZjNHJRC65so.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170915105037XxRIcg6Dy1UBLnMs.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/201709151050487catyNsqvwFSuUWR.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170915105050LPqadiVhfGc15v